{"tid":1534712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"清潔工人職工會：53清潔工曾吸入催淚煙","createTime":"2019-09-03T05:49:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T06:52:40.000Z","uid":212626,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9d02e624ff19cb62749aecf4fd4dfc1a4ec2c41c","tid":1534712,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:49:56.000Z","msg":"清潔工人職工會調查發現，在9個警方曾施放催淚彈的區域，共75名食環署外判清潔工，在工作期間曾經遇過警方施放催淚彈，有53人曾吸入催淚煙，其餘指不知道那些是催淚煙氣味。<br />\n<br />\n受訪工人中，約三成曾出現眼睛乾澀、兩成人有氣管不適、2人指曾經皮膚敏感。調查同時指出，清潔工全部無任何保護裝備。<br />\n<br />\n工會到金鐘食環署總部遞交請願信，要求署方跟進。組織幹事梁芷茵表示，不少清潔工是中老年人士或尼泊爾裔工人，他們不掌握催淚煙禍害，有工人在警方施放催淚彈時，被困於工作的公廁，甚至被迫要在公廁過夜。<br />\n<br />\n工會要求署方為工人提供N95口罩、手套、眼罩等基本裝備，甚至應考慮成立特別清潔隊，處理曾受催淚煙影響的範圍。署方亦應給予清晰指引，在緊急情況下，清潔工可離開工作崗位，而不會被視作擅離職守，也不會被扣工資。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2239975/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2239975%2F&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFC3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9e411344\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2239975/</a>"},{"pid":"72f8116d339d833a5e3e8681aaac8b45507812e0","tid":1534712,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:17.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f0883ea30cdef901c2c6016618cc82725be505c6","tid":1534712,"uid":40839,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:50:50.000Z","msg":"N95<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a31c820d3700f3275c1bda022c389c916a2343c2","tid":1534712,"uid":229436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"得n95 做清潔真係地低泥<br />\nd狗就全身成萬蚊裝備<br />\n清潔工就全身夾埋100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be98cef48ded55906818f2a976bcd589b954de66","tid":1534712,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a31c820d3700f3275c1bda022c389c916a2343c2","tid":1534712,"uid":229436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"得n95 做清潔真係地低泥<br />\nd狗就全身成萬蚊裝備<br />\n清潔工就全身夾埋100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:51:44.000Z","msg":"依個就係政府講的愛香港"},{"pid":"7df850ee561ff7d2db5b389723db4e0d99eeec11","tid":1534712,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:52:12.000Z","msg":"推！<br />\n捐咩錢備女神像，捐備哩啲仲好"},{"pid":"f5d93355b2c7dd50d48eebd26df108052756f97a","tid":1534712,"uid":11454,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"be98cef48ded55906818f2a976bcd589b954de66","tid":1534712,"uid":229436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a31c820d3700f3275c1bda022c389c916a2343c2","tid":1534712,"uid":229436,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T05:51:28.000Z","msg":"得n95 做清潔真係地低泥<br />\nd狗就全身成萬蚊裝備<br />\n清潔工就全身夾埋100蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hk